window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>An ambitious young woman has just one chance to secure her future and reclaim her family's priceless lost artifacts in this stand-alone novel set in the world of the award-winning, </b><b><i>New York Times </i></b><b>bestselling Imperial Radch trilogy.</b></p> <p>Though she knows her brother holds her mother's favor, Ingrid is determined to at least be considered as heir to the family name. She hatches an audacious planâ€”free a thief from a prison planet from which no one has ever returned, and use them to help steal back a priceless artifact.</p> <p>But Ingray and her charge return to her home to find their planet in political turmoil, at the heart of an escalating interstellar conflict. Together, they must make a new plan to salvage Ingray's future and her world, before they are lost to her for good.</p>"; 
